data.description: Take Notice Of This Lovely Custom Low Maintenance Home In A Park Like Setting Just On The Outskirts Of Town. All The Special Touches Makes This Truly A Home You Would Want To Come Home To. Owners Have Took Special Care Of This Immaculate Home That Has Never Been On The Market. One Level Living With 3 Bedrooms And 2 Full Baths. Home Is Adorned With Custom Moldings, Maple Kitchen Cabinets, A Beautifully Tiled Custom Shower, Ceramic Tile And Hardwood Throughout, A Heated And Cooled Detached Garage With Office/storage Room. Included Is An Improved Additional Lot That Is Attached To The Property.
